casebody.data:
No. 11-6783. Marie Assa’ad-Faltas, Petitioner v. Barney Giese, et al. 565 U.S. 1090, 132 S. Ct. 849,

181 L. Ed. 2d 546,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8971. December 12, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of South Carolina dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
